### 5. `.gitignore`
To keep your Git repository clean, create this file in the root folder:

```text
# Ignore compiled binaries
*.out
*.exe
*.o
*.so

# Ignore Jupyter Notebook checkpoints
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Ignore Python cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Ignore heavy datasets
workspace/data/
*.csv
*.h5
*.pt
*.pth
